He's a day's ride from here.

1195
01:37:13,033 --> 01:37:15,020
確定了她安全以後，他才會過來
As soon as she's safe, he will come.

1196
01:37:15,027 --> 01:37:18,054
先給你聖劍，沒有劍，他就不能對你造成威脅
He poses no threat to you without the sword.

1197
01:37:19,034 --> 01:37:21,014
告訴他，明天必須趕到
Tomorrow.

1198
01:37:21,021 --> 01:37:24,001
相信你也知道
I don't have to remind you of what will happen

1199
01:37:24,008 --> 01:37:25,068
要是他不來的話
if he doesn't come.

1200
01:37:26,071 --> 01:37:29,048
那個小男孩會有怎樣的下場
I'll start with the little boy.

1201
01:37:29,055 --> 01:37:31,065
帶上這個女人，走吧
Now, take the girl and go.

1202
01:37:39,076 --> 01:37:43,030
這種蛇毒能讓你看見隱藏的東西
This venom will induce that which is hidden from you.

1203
01:37:43,036 --> 01:37:47,013
能讓你看見一些你不想看見的東西
It will show you things you do not want to see.

1204
01:37:47,020 --> 01:37:49,087
但這對你來說很有用
But you'll need its protection.

1205
01:37:49,094 --> 01:37:51,077
握住我的手
Hold my hand.

1206
01:37:59,091 --> 01:38:01,011
我討厭蛇
I don't like snakes.

1207
01:38:01,018 --> 01:38:03,032
大家都討厭蛇
No one likes snakes.

1208
01:38:11,019 --> 01:38:12,079
握住我的手
Stay with me.

1209
01:38:16,023 --> 01:38:17,046
握住我的手
Stay with me.

1210
01:38:23,027 --> 01:38:26,094
藥效會持續幾個小時
You will feel it for a few hours.

1211
01:38:27,001 --> 01:38:32,085
歌詞大意：年輕的獵人狩獵歸來，虛弱而又貧乏無力
Young man came from hunting faint and weary

1212
01:38:35,041 --> 01:38:40,099
我最親愛的你，是何物在折磨著我的上帝？
What does ail My Lord, my dearie?

1213
01:38:46,093 --> 01:38:52,063
我親愛的兄弟，請鋪好我的床
O brother dear, let my bed be made

1214
01:38:55,000 --> 01:39:00,084
龍葵帶來的絞痛使我不安
For I feel the gripe of the woody nightshade

1215
01:39:05,014 --> 01:39:11,014
這個獵人的生命即將逝去
This young man, he died fair soon

1216
01:39:11,068 --> 01:39:16,052
在獵人的宏月輝茫之下
By the light of the hunters' moon

1217
01:39:16,059 --> 01:39:20,069
弩箭不會上膛
'Twas not by bolt Nor yet by blade

1218
01:39:22,056 --> 01:39:27,067
但我將舉起那用木龍葵漿果塗抹的劍
Oh, the berries of the woody nightshade

1219
01:39:27,073 --> 01:39:32,071
親愛的父親寧和地躺在這裡
?Oh, father dear, lie heavy safe

1220
01:39:34,064 --> 01:39:37,081
在這惡魔鋪就的路上
From the power that the devil made

1221
01:39:43,082 --> 01:39:47,002
路上...
Made

1222
01:40:03,084 --> 01:40:05,011
站住
That's far enough.

1223
01:40:07,077 --> 01:40:10,038
讓我們了結這一切吧
Let's get this done quickly, shall we?

1224
01:40:10,044 --> 01:40:11,081
讓他跪下
Put him on his knees.

1225
01:40:13,038 --> 01:40:15,008
讓他跪下！
Put him on his knees!

1226
01:41:47,034 --> 01:41:48,054
拿起武器，跟他們拼了！
Go, go, go!

1227
01:42:09,029 --> 01:42:12,023
你知道你要付出怎樣的代價的
You know the price.

1228
01:42:24,038 --> 01:42:25,078
爸爸，發生什麼事了
Father, what's happening?

1229
01:42:26,035 --> 01:42:27,065
你們兩個出去
Leave.

1230
01:42:35,062 --> 01:42:37,012
你臉上的血是怎麼回事
Why is there blood on your face?

1231
01:42:40,046 --> 01:42:42,010
發生什麼事了
What's going on?

1232
01:42:50,007 --> 01:42:52,001
爸爸，你這樣把我嚇壞了
Father, you're scaring me.

1233
01:42:57,091 --> 01:42:59,095
我真的很愛你
I love you very much.

1234
01:43:37,022 --> 01:43:38,089
沖啊！
Come on!

1235
01:43:43,049 --> 01:43:44,069
沖啊！
Charge!

1236
01:47:20,021 --> 01:47:24,034
侄子，你贏了
You have won, nephew.

1237
01:47:34,032 --> 01:47:37,056
看上去你確實贏了
You have won.

1238
01:47:44,043 --> 01:47:47,043
但你還沒有擊敗我
Now, play with me.

1239
01:48:48,043 --> 01:48:52,090
看來，這把劍要屬於我了
I think that sword belongs to me now.

1240
01:48:59,057 --> 01:49:01,001
快跑，兒子！
Run, son!

1241
01:49:12,082 --> 01:49:14,055
弟弟
Brother...

1242
01:49:15,092 --> 01:49:19,029
看來，這把劍要屬於我了
I think that sword belongs to me now.

1243
01:49:19,036 --> 01:49:21,043
你所付出的代價
Whatever price you paid,

1244
01:49:21,049 --> 01:49:24,006
遠超你所得到的一切
it will be more than you know.

1245
01:49:29,084 --> 01:49:32,027
兒子，你不需要再逃跑了
You don't need to run anymore.

1246
01:49:36,018 --> 01:49:38,071
你不需要再逃避自己的過去了
You don't need to look away.

1247
01:49:50,059 --> 01:49:52,063
聖劍歸你了
The sword is yours, son.

1248
01:49:54,073 --> 01:49:55,076
拿起它
Take it.

1249
01:50:28,059 --> 01:50:31,073
你之前問我，是什麼撐起了我的野心
You wanted to know what gave me such drive.

1250
01:50:36,073 --> 01:50:38,017
我現在可以告訴你，是你撐起了我的野心
It was you.

1251
01:50:44,011 --> 01:50:46,005
是你害得我成為孤兒，在妓院里長大
You put me in that brothel.

1252
01:50:54,005 --> 01:50:56,012
是你害得我我流落街頭
You cut me on the streets.

1253
01:51:04,040 --> 01:51:07,047
我之所以會有今天，都是因為你
I am here now because of you.

1254
01:52:04,062 --> 01:52:06,056
你
You

1255
01:52:06,063 --> 01:52:08,026
造就了我
created me.

1256
01:52:33,002 --> 01:52:34,005
為此
And, for that...

1257
01:52:34,012 --> 01:52:35,082
我向你致敬
I bless you.

1258
01:52:39,076 --> 01:52:42,039
你讓我的奮鬥有了意義
You make sense of the devil.

1259
01:54:10,072 --> 01:54:11,072
拉弓！
Nock!

1260
01:54:14,099 --> 01:54:16,022
點火！
Light!

1261
01:54:20,023 --> 01:54:21,059
準備！
Ready!

1262
01:54:25,073 --> 01:54:26,073
放箭！
Loose!

1263
01:54:49,022 --> 01:54:51,036
我知道
While I understand there's been a change

1264
01:54:51,042 --> 01:54:54,009
雖然貴國的國君有所更替
in the leadership of this nation...

1265
01:54:54,016 --> 01:54:56,066
但我相信您仍然會遵守
I am confident that you will still honor the agreement

1266
01:54:56,073 --> 01:55:01,010
前任國君同我國國君達成的協議
made by your predecessor and my king.

1267
01:55:01,017 --> 01:55:02,050
根據協議
We expect to leave here

1268
01:55:02,057 --> 01:55:05,037
我們要運走一萬名年輕男子
with 10,000 young men
as agreed.

1269
01:55:05,044 --> 01:55:07,027
伙計，這事我不同意
Yeah, I don't think so, mate.

1270
01:55:08,014 --> 01:55:09,034
您說什麼？
Excuse me?

1271
01:55:11,074 --> 01:55:13,055
我剛剛說，這事我不同意
I said, "I don't think so, mate".

1272
01:55:16,061 --> 01:55:19,035
我們在這乾啥來著？
We've been wondering what you were doing in here.

1273
01:55:20,015 --> 01:55:21,065
這玩意看上去很有趣
I like it.

1274
01:55:23,026 --> 01:55:24,046
這是啥？
What is it?

1275
01:55:25,019 --> 01:55:26,032
對啊，我也問，這是什麼？
Yes, what is it?

1276
01:55:26,039 --> 01:55:28,076
這是一塊放圓形奶酪的大轉盤？
A carousel? A giant wheel of cheese?

1277
01:55:28,083 --> 01:55:30,043
你準備拿這玩意乾啥？
What are you supposed to do with it?

1278
01:55:30,050 --> 01:55:32,003
我懂了
I know.

1279
01:55:32,010 --> 01:55:33,047
這是個舞池
It's a dance floor.

1280
01:55:33,053 --> 01:55:35,060
等把它修好了
And once you finish it

1281
01:55:35,067 --> 01:55:37,037
我們要怎麼把它運到舞廳中間
how are you supposed to get to the middle?

1282
01:55:37,044 --> 01:55:38,090
我們要怎麼把它搬過去
But how did you get it through the door?

1283
01:55:38,097 --> 01:55:41,041
是抬著走還是滾著走？
Did you carry it in? Or did you roll it in?

1284
01:55:41,047 --> 01:55:42,087
我想提醒一下陛下
May I remind you

1285
01:55:42,094 --> 01:55:46,041
我們有三千艘作戰船隻
a fleet of 3,000 longships controlling the seas,

1286
01:55:46,048 --> 01:55:47,085
掌控著貴國周邊海域的制海權
surrounding your island.

1287
01:55:47,091 --> 01:55:51,082
我建議您不要得罪我們
It would be unwise to displease my king.

1288
01:55:52,032 --> 01:55:53,052
那真是不好意思了
I'm sorry.

1289
01:55:56,082 --> 01:56:00,039
喬治，威特，珀西，請行跪拜禮
George, Wet Stick, Percy, on your knees.

1290
01:56:01,039 --> 01:56:02,086
貝德維爾爵士，有勞你主持儀式了
Sir Bedivere, if you would?

1291
01:56:05,026 --> 01:56:08,033
我可以給貴國寬限一周的時間
I'm prepared to extend the deadline by a week.

1292
01:56:08,040 --> 01:56:09,060
我說了不行，就是不行
No.

1293
01:56:10,030 --> 01:56:12,000
我再說一遍
I mean, I'm sorry.

1294
01:56:12,007 --> 01:56:13,067
別搞錯了，現在時局變了
You've made a mistake.

1295
01:56:13,074 --> 01:56:15,054
我和伏提庚很不一樣
You're no longer dealing with the man

1296
01:56:15,061 --> 01:56:17,061
他受到人民的唾棄
you previously met.

1297
01:56:18,041 --> 01:56:22,085
而我，受人民擁戴
You are addressing England

1298
01:56:22,091 --> 01:56:27,009
我代表的是全英格蘭的人民
and all the subjects under her king's protection.

1299
01:56:27,015 --> 01:56:29,039
起身，喬治爵士
Arise, Sir George.

1300
01:56:29,045 --> 01:56:31,019
現在你最好
So you have a choice.

1301
01:56:31,026 --> 01:56:34,013
向全英格蘭人民行跪拜禮
You can now kneel to England...

1302
01:56:35,033 --> 01:56:37,060
起身，特裡斯坦爵士
Arise, Sir Tristan.

1303
01:56:37,066 --> 01:56:40,010
要不然我就不客氣了
Or I'll step off this throne,

1304
01:56:40,016 --> 01:56:43,080
你可以試試看，要是你再用跟伏提庚打交道的方式，和我打交道
and you can deal with me as the man you previously met.

1305
01:56:45,040 --> 01:56:46,087
起身，珀西瓦爾爵士
Arise, Sir Percival.

1306
01:56:50,068 --> 01:56:52,095
會有怎樣的後果
And we can see how that goes.

1307
01:56:58,098 --> 01:57:00,039
威廉爵士
Sir William.

1308
01:57:01,059 --> 01:57:03,039
你來主持我的儀式吧
If you would?

1309
01:57:05,006 --> 01:57:06,049
榮幸之至
It would be my honor.

1310
01:57:29,085 --> 01:57:32,022
這不挺好的?，起身
Well, now that's out the way,

1311
01:57:32,028 --> 01:57:33,069
大家坐下來吃飯
let's eat.

1312
01:57:37,056 --> 01:57:38,082
既然能當朋友
Why have enemies

1313
01:57:39,076 --> 01:57:41,066
又何必樹敵呢
when you can have friends?

1314
01:57:46,056 --> 01:57:49,003
起身，陛下
Arise, my king.

1315
01:58:01,021 --> 01:58:02,058
亞瑟王
King Arthur.

1316
01:58:09,079 --> 01:58:11,066
這不是舞池，這是張圓桌
It's a table.

1317
01:58:12,042 --> 01:58:14,013
我們可以圍坐在圓桌邊，討論事情
You sit at it.

1318
01:58:37,035 --> 01:58:39,028
天佑吾王！
Long live the King!

1319
01:58:39,045 --> 01:58:41,052
吾王萬歲！
Long live the King!


